<br>
The more believable sources say that the minis are on a 30-minute spawn cycle with placeholders.  If this is true, then  I don't see a reason to put them on rotation.<br>
<br>
Other people have said they are on a 24-hour cycle, which lends to a rotation being a good thing.<br>
<br>
My guess is that some minis are the former and others are the latter.  Until there is no doubt what the spawn-cycle is like for all the minis, and there is no doubt about what can drop what epic pieces, KGC taking a vote on what to do with PoH would be premature.<br>
<br>
The reason for the rotations would be to insure that people get a chance at epic drops, and if we don't *know* how the epic drop mobs work yet, then we can't cast an intelligent vote. <p>Zymyool, Officer of the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.ancientadventurers.org"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Ancient Adventurers</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> on the Karana Server<br>
