<br>
They aren't on rotation for valid reasons.  Fast repop or only dropping one epic piece for one class seem to be the main reasons.  (And of course, critters that are spawned aren't on rotation, e.g., Faydedar, Ragefire, several of the monk fights).<br>
<br>
Restricting the minis while keeping the plane as a whole open is basically just a death sentence to whatever puller accidentally aggroes them.<br>
<br>
Since the minis don't necessarily drop anything and the yard trash supposedly does, it doesn't make sense to me to restrict them in any way, unless you restrict the whole plane, which would be a huge waste given the repop rate.<br>
<br>
